abstract: As a top American envoy visits the region, the North declared that tests would bolster its “reliable strategic nuclear deterrent.”
snippet: As a top American envoy visits the region, the North declared that tests would bolster its “reliable strategic nuclear deterrent.”
lead_paragraph: SEOUL, South Korea — A second test of what appeared to be an advanced missile engine, part of what North Korea said on Saturday was part of a “reliable strategic nuclear deterrent,” left little doubt that the country is moving quickly toward resuming the program that led to a crisis with Washington two years ago.

abstract: With a record number of asylum seekers, France is getting tough on immigration. But 450 squatters find shelter in a school building in Lyon.
snippet: With a record number of asylum seekers, France is getting tough on immigration. But 450 squatters find shelter in a school building in Lyon.
lead_paragraph: LYON, France — From their villages and towns in West Africa, the squatters had crossed deserts, seas and mountains to arrive in Lyon, most of them for no specific reason.

lead_paragraph: DES MOINES, Iowa — Kim Motl doesn’t work in the health insurance industry. But her friends and neighbors do. So when she saw Sen.
